{
  "page": "Greensight",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg/350px-Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"263\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg/525px-Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg/700px-Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Kristina_Carroll_greendream.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Three-eyed crow\">Three-eyed crow</a> comes to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> in a green dream. By Kristina Carroll © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>greensight</b> is the ability to have <a href=\"/index.php/Dreams_and_prophecies\" title=\"Dreams and prophecies\">prophetic dreams</a> called <b>green dreams</b> (also called <b>greendreams</b>). \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#About\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">About</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Known_Greendreamers\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Greendreamers</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"About\">About</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greensight&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: About\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>A person with the greensight may dream as other people do, but the green dreams are different, filled with symbolic meaning, images, and metaphors of what is to come.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The meaning behind the dreams is not always obvious, but the dreamer experiences the fulfillment of visions in the unfolding of events. Supposedly these dreams can concern the dreamer or another person, but the dreamer will be able to tell the difference. Greenseers might also dream of their own deaths. <a href=\"/index.php/Warg\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Warg\">Wargs</a> have been known to also possess this ability.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Greenseer\" title=\"Greenseer\">Greenseers</a>, the wise men of the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>, reputedly possessed the greensight. Some <a href=\"/index.php/Crannogmen\" title=\"Crannogmen\">crannogmen</a> are also known to have the greensight. One of them is <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a>, who has unnaturally green eyes. It is possible that this is the result of his advanced greensight abilities.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Greendreamers\">Known Greendreamers</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greensight&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Greendreamers\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greensight&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Greenseer\" title=\"Greenseer\">Greenseer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">Skinchanger</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_dreams\" title=\"Dragon dreams\">Dragon dreams</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greensight&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">My brother</a> has the greensight. He dreams things that haven't happened, but sometimes they do.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I dreamed of a <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">winged wolf</a> bound to earth with grey stone chains. It was a green dream, so I knew it was true. A <a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Three-eyed crow\">crow</a> was trying to peck through the chains, but the stone was too hard and his beak could only chip at them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">He</a> had had a green dream, he said, and his green dreams did not lie.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>, about <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote> \n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Greensight&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok28.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_28\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 28\">Chapter 28</a>, Bran IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Bran III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_56\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 56\">Chapter 56</a>, Bran IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404043141\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.023 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.024 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 570/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8876/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3376/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 900/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2249/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   14.109      1 -total\n 75.33%   10.629      6 Template:Ref\n 45.47%    6.416      6 Template:Ref/core\n 36.91%    5.208      3 Template:Quote\n 15.41%    2.174      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:1593-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404043141 and revision id 324281\n -->\n",
